un3=. p,un2			NB. new units
NB. 	smoutput z ,: ".each z=. ;:'x y un0 un2 un3 f0 fx p'
un3 changeunits y
nb 'item' ; y ; '-units changed from:' ; un0 ; 'to:' ; un3
  NB. Scaling prefixes recognised above:
  NB.	------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  NB. 	deca- 	hecto- 	kilo- 	mega- 	giga- 	tera- 	peta- 	exa- 	zetta- 	yotta-
